reviewText: ok, i just ordered the hi-8 adbventures so i couldn't tell ya how it is.... all i know is that millencolin is the best band alive and no one can beat them.

The Answer is YES! If you are a Millencolin fan, there is no other way than to get your fix of the band through this video. There are 23 songs on this tape, which include live performances of many of the songs. Lots of  cool clips of concerts,skateboarding,Millencolin in the studio and them  hanging out. So if you are a Millencolin fan, fork out the cash and buy  this video, you Softcore fans won't be disapointed.
